p: Data sets were analyzed with GraphPad Prism software (GraphPad Software, Inc.). A two-way ANOVA followed by Tukeyâ€™s multiple-comparison test was used to determine significant differences in gene expression and cytokine production by DCs. Statistical significances between viral groups (human or avian NS1 viruses) in gene expression and cytokine production by NHBE cells were determined using a t test. Correlation analyses were performed using R, version 3.3.1, and Rstudio.
